WEBVTT

00:00:01.200 --> 00:00:04.199
Hello, this is
Jérôme Lepagnol.

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:06.489
I am candidate for election
of the administrator

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:10.289
representing employees
SG Group shareholders

00:00:10.300 --> 00:00:12.689
with Caroline Le Vaillant
as a replacement.

00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:17.199
The objective of this video is
double on the one hand,

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:19.388
I would like you to have
awareness of the stakes of this

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:21.699
election for the bank and
on the other hand,

00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:23.688
I would like to explain to you in
what our proposal

00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:28.388
different from those of others
candidates. Let me talk to you

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:32.489
about the importance for
this bank of this election

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:34.489
Voting for this election,
it's a little bit like saying

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:37.489
"I would like the good sense of
the fields be more visible

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:39.789
and be taken into account
at the executive level

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:43.699
officers and board of directors".

00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:46.189
And if it was you, yes you!
who was at the helm

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:48.589
As you know, we are in
budget phase and those who

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:52.189
practice this exercise
know how difficult it is

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:53.989
but you, you know

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:56.689
where the savings are, where
put the budgetary efforts

00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:57.699
and the means.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:01.089
And if you were the
manager who makes the

00:01:01.100 --> 00:01:02.489
budget trade-offs?

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:05.089
There is a budgetary dimension
but also human.

00:01:05.100 --> 00:01:07.599
Well, voting for this election,
it's a little bit like saying

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:11.288
"I would like the people, the
teams that make up this bank

00:01:11.300 --> 00:01:12.589
be considered because it is

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:15.788
great lever for the
bank vis-à-vis its

00:01:15.800 --> 00:01:17.199
customers and all our
ecosystem.

00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:21.489
We will soon be in phase
annual evaluation.  You, you

00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:24.788
know how to make progess the
people who need it and

00:01:24.800 --> 00:01:27.689
desire it and above all you know
how to motivate and engage

00:01:27.700 --> 00:01:28.788
teams for the bank.

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:32.889
And if you were the kind manager
who is watching after this?

00:01:32.900 --> 00:01:37.889
Banking consolidation at
European level is already in

00:01:37.900 --> 00:01:39.799
progress, for example this Friday

00:01:39.800 --> 00:01:43.698
September 18 in Spain CAIXABANK
(30000 collaborators) and BANKIA (15000)

00:01:43.710 --> 00:01:47.689
have seen their merger
approved by their

00:01:47.700 --> 00:01:51.889
respective boards of directors.
What about us? One day

00:01:51.900 --> 00:01:54.788
or the other our bank will/may
also be concerned

00:01:54.800 --> 00:01:56.299
by any of these
positions.

00:01:56.900 --> 00:01:59.288
Well, voting for this
election a little bit to say

00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:03.288
"I love this company and I
would like that in this

00:02:03.300 --> 00:02:06.189
uncertain environment the
good choices be made for

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:08.899
the strategic decisions of
the bank."

00:02:08.900 --> 00:02:13.489
You, you know what it takes
absolutely to be valued in the

00:02:13.500 --> 00:02:15.589
bank, which represents a
competitive advantage, a

00:02:15.600 --> 00:02:19.789
gem; you know the
segments (customers, products,

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:24.989
or services) it would be necessary to abandon
redesign or develop. And as

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:27.889
citizen or as a consumer of
banking services, you are

00:02:27.900 --> 00:02:29.099
sensitive to the fact that everything

00:02:29.100 --> 00:02:32.289
this implies remain in the interest of
our world in the long term.

00:02:32.300 --> 00:02:35.399
What if you were the strategist
of such a merger?

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:40.099
The election is important for
you and the bank.
